South African Gold Production Fell 5.8% in May From Year Ago, Agency Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-14T09:30:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/south-african-gold-production-fell-5-8-in-may-from-year-ago-agency-says.html
South African  gold production  fell
5.8 percent in May from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre Terblanche,
a spokesman for Statistics South  Africa , said by phone from
 Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
